A3: q is  first-col-of-circulant;
A4: (( CCirc q ) is_col_circulant_about q & ( Indices ( CCirc p ) ) = ( Indices ( CCirc q ) )) by A1,A3,CKB13:def 1,MATRIX_1:26;
