A12: (for i,j being Nat holds ([ i,j ] in ( Indices ( CCirc p ) ) implies ( ( CCirc ( p + q ) ) * (i,j) ) = ( ( ( CCirc p ) * (i,j) ) + ( ( CCirc q ) * (i,j) ) )))
proof
