assume A13: [ i,j ] in ( Indices ( CCirc p ) );
then A14: ( ( ( i - j ) mod n ) + 1 ) in ( Seg n ) by A9,CKB3:1;
( ( CCirc ( p + q ) ) * (i,j) ) = ( ( p + q ) . ( ( ( i - j ) mod ( len ( p + q ) ) ) + 1 ) ) by A5,A11,A13,CKB9:def 1
.= ( (the addF of K) . (( p . ( ( ( i - j ) mod ( len ( p + q ) ) ) + 1 ) ),( q . ( ( ( i - j ) mod ( len ( p + q ) ) ) + 1 ) )) ) by A8,A10,A14,FUNCOP_1:22
.= ( (the addF of K) . (( ( CCirc p ) * (i,j) ),( q . ( ( ( i - j ) mod ( len q ) ) + 1 ) )) ) by A1,A10,A7,A13,CKB9:def 1
.= ( ( ( CCirc p ) * (i,j) ) + ( ( CCirc q ) * (i,j) ) ) by A4,A13,CKB9:def 1;
hence thesis;
end;
